snippet.title: Understanding the Vocabulary of Algebra For Dummies
snippet.description: Knowing the symbols and expressions used in algebra makes understanding algebra easier. This video explains some common algebra symbols and phrases, such equations, operations, variables, and constants. No more confusion!
